A lot of these IDs start with a digit so you won&#39;t be able to use them as CSS selectors as is, but you could use something like `&lt;button id=&quot;coinid-${coins[i].id}&quot; class=&quot;moreInfo&quot;&gt;More Info&lt;/button&gt;` inside the loop.

Inside your click handler you can then reference the id of each button:

    let btnid = e.target.id;
