The only way to capture the Request with guzzle is to create the request yourself and send it to guzzle.

```
  $request = new Request(&#39;put&#39;, $endpoint, $headers, $body, &quot;1.1&quot;);
  $response = $this-&gt;client-&gt;send($request);
